item.title: BD Diesel 1054525XM3 X-Power Plus w/3-in-1 X Monitor - Dodge 2004.5-2005 600 series
item.description: X-Power Plus module for the 2003-2005 Dodge-Cummins offers what no other electronic performance product can: State-of-the-art technology, serious power and ultimate controlall without compromise! Unlike other products that raise fuel pressure to increase fuel delivery (which can cause leaks and damage to fuel system components), the X-Power Plus achieves performance gains by altering injector pulse duration and timing. A stronger, longer combustion event means more boost and more powerup to 180 HP at the rear wheels! A cab-mounted, color-coded Power Dial allows progressive control in any one of three power levels. Comes complete with BD's 3-in-1 X-Monitor digital gauge pack.
